Actress Tonto Dikeh has reacted to claims by her ex- best friend Bobrisky that she was arrested in Dubai for the possession of weed. Bobrisky had alleged the actress was jailed after she was caught dead drunk and with weed. But the actress claimed that she was arrested for illegal filming and rudeness to a security agent. She reiterated that the punishment for possession of drugs in Dubai is 4-6 years, stating she would have been jailed for that long if the accusation was true. She said: “Education is very important in life. If Bob had known that weed smokers in Dubai are liable to 4-6 years in jail. If you like be the President’s daughter. As a matter of fact, the ruler of Dubai has his own daughter in jail for lesser crimes going 7 years now.   Baba Fryo hints on new single release     Bobrisky accuses Tonto Dikeh of diverting foundation…     Comic voice over artiste King Kong’s son turns one   “You wouldn’t disgrace your family with such horrible lies. Who went to jail in Dubai bob? “Plus my altercations with the authorities in Dubai were recorded and posted on every bog in the country. “Lucky enough, Dubai has public records accessible to the public in my case which was illegal filming and abusive words to a security. “Bob get a life and at least treat your maggot infested butt “In a nutshell, illiteracy is a disease.”